939
01:13:09,429 --> 01:13:12,973
I could only take the
gentle styles like Tai Chi Chuan.

940
01:13:17,647 --> 01:13:20,980
Who would have thought that
a couple years later,

941
01:13:21,108 --> 01:13:23,771
