1006
01:16:28,504 --> 01:16:29,625
Ah, Ah..., shut up, just keep going.

1007
01:16:45,270 --> 01:16:46,101
Grandma!

1008
01:16:46,230 --> 01:16:47,431
Grandpa!

1009
01:17:10,087 --> 01:17:12,169
