1017
01:17:38,699 --> 01:17:40,160
No one wants me.

1018
01:17:40,743 --> 01:17:43,536
We're out for fun,
why get mad at the kids?

1019
01:17:44,955 --> 01:17:46,877
How can you be so
developed in Kung Fu

1020
01:17:46,999 --> 01:17:48,791
