1201
01:27:50,895 --> 01:27:51,596
You volunteered? Fine!

1202
01:27:51,729 --> 01:27:52,730
He asked for help, fine!

1203
01:27:52,855 --> 01:27:55,027
I don't care.
I can't take any risks tonight.

1204
01:27:55,149 --> 01:27:55,640
Liu

1205
