1294
01:33:30,610 --> 01:33:32,982
Shirley, I'm standing in
front of the Lai Fu restaurant.

1295
01:33:33,112 --> 01:33:34,784
The owner Frankie Huang tried to fire

1296
01:33:34,905 --> 01:33:36,406
