1329
01:36:03,345 --> 01:36:05,267
Mine is yours.

1330
01:36:06,098 --> 01:36:08,981
Forget it. I see clearly now,

1331
01:36:10,144 --> 01:36:12,977
the only thing that matters

1332
01:36:13,105 --> 01:36:15,397
